 138:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c **** /** @defgroup USARTEx_Exported_Functions_Group2 Peripheral Control functions
 139:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****   * @brief    Extended Peripheral Control functions
