 145:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****     [..] This section provides the following functions:
 146:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****      (+) HAL_USARTEx_EnableSPISlaveMode() API enables the SPI slave mode
 147:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****      (+) HAL_USARTEx_DisableSPISlaveMode() API disables the SPI slave mode
 148:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****      (+) HAL_USARTEx_ConfigNSS API configures the Slave Select input pin (NSS)
 149:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****      (+) HAL_USARTEx_EnableFifoMode() API enables the FIFO mode
 150:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****      (+) HAL_USARTEx_DisableFifoMode() API disables the FIFO mode
 151:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****      (+) HAL_USARTEx_SetTxFifoThreshold() API sets the TX FIFO threshold
 152:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****      (+) HAL_USARTEx_SetRxFifoThreshold() API sets the RX FIFO threshold
 153:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c **** 
 154:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c **** 
 155:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c **** @endverbatim
 156:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart_ex.c ****   * @{
